{"tid":2127794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛：憂慮香港疫情影響大","createTime":"2020-07-27T13:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T20:27:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":26,"dislike":597,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"9e81caaf145348b338e944158e88d21e88642708","tid":2127794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540195-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540195-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=91216e38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540195-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fbcca26e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540195-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n世衛突發事件委員會今個星期將會再次開會，評估新型肺炎疫情大流行。世衛總幹事譚德塞說，中國、加拿大、德國及南韓已經控制著疫情，雖然全球付出巨大努力，但前方仍然有很長的路要走。<br />\n<br />\n世衛緊急項目技術主管范科霍夫說，香港出現疫情復發，部分個案出現在護理場所，認為病毒有機會再次在社區傳播。她說，正如在很多國家見到，如果病毒傳入院舍，可以造成毀滅性影響，世衛已經發布指引，亦有與香港很多人合作，相信香港憑著應對包括沙士等傳染病的豐富經驗，可以成功控制疫情。"},{"pid":"0459cdfde8ddb7911e763364821e1e746329049c","tid":2127794,"uid":248270,"like":401,"dislike":3,"score":398,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"世衛幾時收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f6f071407fe0eae5f37207ee4b26b15cfc8125","tid":2127794,"uid":362492,"like":42,"dislike":303,"score":-261,"citedBy":22,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33116a598680b1fd402be756bd4743f045d2b2df","tid":2127794,"uid":60129,"like":139,"dislike":2,"score":137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"好耶 變左香港肺炎<br />\n<br />\n大大又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dcd7eb4f55638d35518da82f339b3560c29b72","tid":2127794,"uid":51271,"like":114,"dislike":3,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTi