"msg":"fuck off , Corrupted Heath office"},{"pid":"aa8f8a06ec1d684d4a4fb9a316625bb36805847d","tid":2127794,"uid":363275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e81caaf145348b338e944158e88d21e88642708","tid":2127794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540195-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540195-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=91216e38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540195-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fbcca26e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540195-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n世衛突發事件委員會今個星期將會再次開會，評估新型肺炎疫情大流行。世衛總幹事譚德塞說，中國、加拿大、德國及南韓已經控制著疫情，雖然全球付出巨大努力，但前方仍然有很長的路要走。<br />\n<br />\n世衛緊急項目技術主管范科霍夫說，香港出現疫情復發，部分個案出現在護理場所，認為病毒有機會再次在社區傳播。她說，正如在很多國家見到，如果病毒傳入院舍，可以造成毀滅性影響，世衛已經發布指引，亦有與香港很多人合作，相信香港憑著應對包括沙士等傳染病的豐富經驗，可以成功控制疫情。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"其實香港🇭🇰都係得2000單<br />\n跟其他國家相比起.....<br />\n其實好小姐"},{"pid":"14b8a22618a2235496213a6a7d1672013a44bd3b","tid":2127794,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"算數啦，世衛咪又係中國啲馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bad29c9b7dd3d766e0557122a60758a712645b3","tid":2127794,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"唔知部MacBook Air有冇買AppleCare+呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96e4e17b9d13a9fd9e799a9814a9f0da02bd3bd","tid":2127794,"uid":238773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭黑暗兵法<br />\n<br />\n偷偷地放免檢疫人落嚟，令市區大爆發<br />\n<br />\n1. 進遲立法會選